org.eclipse.keyple.core.card.selection

Class CardSelector

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.keyple.core.card.selection.CardSelector
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class CardSelector
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This POJO holds the information needed to select a particular card.

    In addition to the card protocol provides two optional structure CardSelector.AidSelector and CardSelector.AtrFilter to specify the expected card profile.

    Since:
    0.9
